            "id": "tradingview:da88204f228e7:0",
            "title": "Key facts: XRP Stochastic RSI Hits 0.00; Novogratz Backs Investment; Reserve Inclusion Boosts Wealth",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-KX2tCBZq body-pIO_GYwT content-pIO_GYwT\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-cBh_FN2P logosContainer-cwMMKgmm\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><ul class=\"list-bmN0_SHH list--padded-bmN0_SHH\"><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>XRP's Stochastic RSI has dropped to 0.00 on a 3-week chart, a rare sign that may indicate a price rally, suggesting selling pressure is waning and long-term holders are buying.</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/newsbtc:215b614a1094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">1</span></a></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Galaxy CEO Mike Novogratz has changed his view on XRP, moving from doubt to investment, and commended the robust community supporting the asset amid the SEC lawsuit against Ripple.</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/u_today:3c4ca2278094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">2</span></a></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Joshua Dalton of Triblu noted that XRP holders could gain wealth if XRP is included in a US crypto reserve, citing its ties to a US company as a potential advantage over Bitcoin.</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/newsbtc:3784bb089094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">3</span></a></li></ul></span></div></div>",
            "link": "https://www.tradingview.com/news/tradingview:da88204f228e7:0-key-facts-xrp-stochastic-rsi-hits-0-00-novogratz-backs-investment-reserve-inclusion-boosts-wealth/",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-26 08:03:00",
            "source": "TradingView",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
        },
        {
            "id": "tradingview:77117664b7058:0",
            "title": "Key facts: User loses $50M in Tether attack; 53% of USDT frozen on Tron",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-KX2tCBZq body-pIO_GYwT content-pIO_GYwT\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-cBh_FN2P logosContainer-cwMMKgmm\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><ul class=\"list-bmN0_SHH list--padded-bmN0_SHH\"><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>A user lost almost $50 million in Tether (USDT) from an address poisoning attack, where funds were sent to a fake address mimicking a real one, highlighting blockchain vulnerabilities.</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/u_today:a5fc37946094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">1</span></a></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Over 53% of frozen Tether (USDT) is on the Tron network, known for fast, low-cost transfers. Tether can burn and reissue tokens to address scams.</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/coinpedia:1f5251517094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">2</span></a></li></ul></span></div></div>",
            "link": "https://www.tradingview.com/news/tradingview:77117664b7058:0-key-facts-user-loses-50m-in-tether-attack-53-of-usdt-frozen-on-tron/",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-26 08:03:00",
            "source": "TradingView",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
        },
        {
            "id": "tradingview:0223768080e5f:0",
            "title": "Key facts: Ethereum ETFs Surge; Price Hits Record $4,953.73; ePBS Enhances Security",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-KX2tCBZq body-pIO_GYwT content-pIO_GYwT\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-cBh_FN2P logosContainer-cwMMKgmm\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><ul class=\"list-bmN0_SHH list--padded-bmN0_SHH\"><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>By late 2025, demand for Ethereum ETFs surged, with 11 available, causing a supply squeeze that drove Ethereum's price to a record high of $4,953.73.</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/invezz:20cc596f2094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">1</span></a></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Ethereum continues to lead in the financial ecosystem with a greater total value locked (TVL) and stablecoin usage, despite competition from Solana, which is noted for its speed and adaptability.</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/coinpedia:d5f7f1904094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">2</span></a></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Ethereum's integration of Enshrined Proposer Builder Separation (ePBS) boosts security and decentralization, enabling more time for generating and validating zero-knowledge (ZK) proofs.</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/cointelegraph:7825da4af094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">3</span></a></li></ul></span></div></div>",
            "link": "https://www.tradingview.com/news/tradingview:0223768080e5f:0-key-facts-ethereum-etfs-surge-price-hits-record-4-953-73-epbs-enhances-security/",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-26 08:03:00",
            "source": "TradingView",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
        },
        {
            "id": "tradingview:5dd5fc0c98fbb:0",
            "title": "Key facts: Cardano Price Drop Triggers $167K Liquidations; $50M Loss Reported; Hoskinson Denies ADA Sale Rumors",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-KX2tCBZq body-pIO_GYwT content-pIO_GYwT\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-cBh_FN2P logosContainer-cwMMKgmm\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><ul class=\"list-bmN0_SHH list--padded-bmN0_SHH\"><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Cardano (ADAUSD) saw a significant price drop, leading to $167,850 in long position liquidations within an hour, creating a 66,530% liquidation imbalance against just $243 in shorts.</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/u_today:15d61d1c0094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">1</span></a></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Charles Hoskinson highlighted a $50 million loss from an address poisoning attack, noting that Cardano's UTXO model offers better protection against such scams than Ethereum's account-based model.</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/u_today:a5fc37946094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">2</span></a></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Charles Hoskinson, Cardano's founder, denied rumors of selling ADA tokens at a high price in 2021, claiming he never sold any ADA and calling the allegations false.</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/u_today:315fd15a9094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">3</span></a></li></ul></span></div></div>",
            "link": "https://www.tradingview.com/news/tradingview:5dd5fc0c98fbb:0-key-facts-cardano-price-drop-triggers-167k-liquidations-50m-loss-reported-hoskinson-denies-ada-sale-rumors/",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-26 08:03:00",
            "source": "TradingView",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
        },
        {
            "id": "tradingview:59f528040ea46:0",
            "title": "Key facts: Bitcoin options worth $23.7B expire; ETFs face outflows",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-KX2tCBZq body-pIO_GYwT content-pIO_GYwT\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-cBh_FN2P logosContainer-cwMMKgmm\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><ul class=\"list-bmN0_SHH list--padded-bmN0_SHH\"><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>On December 26, Bitcoin options worth $23.7 billion will expire, likely leading to price stability as institutions adjust their positions to optimize profits.</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/u_today:b80e2b8bb094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">1</span></a></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Bitcoin shows little correlation with the Nasdaq and a negative one with gold, indicating a shift towards being viewed as a high-risk asset, leading to stagnant capital inflows.</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/cryptonews:d1da8a91a094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">2</span></a><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/u_today:4c94f46c9094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">3</span></a></li><li class=\"listItem-bmN0_SHH\"><span>Major Bitcoin Exchange-Traded Funds (ETFs) have experienced continuous outflows since November, reflecting a trend of institutional disengagement from Bitcoin (BTCUSD).</span><a class=\"tag-Jww2aqrB tag-zVPYJd3B xxsmall-zVPYJd3B square-zVPYJd3B interactive-zVPYJd3B apply-overflow-tooltip apply-overflow-tooltip--allow-text apply-overflow-tooltip--check-children\" data-exclude-from-news-link-analytics=\"true\" href=\"/news/zycrypto:76723d014094b:0\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"text-Jww2aqrB\">4</span></a></li></ul></span></div></div>",
            "link": "https://www.tradingview.com/news/tradingview:59f528040ea46:0-key-facts-bitcoin-options-worth-23-7b-expire-etfs-face-outflows/",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-26 08:03:00",
            "source": "TradingView",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
        },
